like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2e65efdbbcd266e061bccdeff2ac1a93cf32cf2","tid":1377553,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:17:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c72ae407f582296cc39d2307c8bc2d1221bafeff","tid":1377553,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82c4c953dc7962cce2a6c9a3edf1caece240f10","tid":1377553,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"轉至PTT：<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1564274134.A.B05.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1564274134.A.B05.html&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=19795db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1564274134.A.B05.html</a><br />\n感謝台仔 唔知有無人有NOWTV本身影到既完整板<br />\n<br />\n大家好，<br />\n以下是熱更多關於香港黑警與黑道勾結的更多證據！<br />\n政府也為了避免社會觀感不佳, 出動社會人士來鎮暴,<br />\n最後在深液還被鏡頭補抓到了警察和當地有力人士,元郎的南邊圍福德堂前聚在一起<br />\n南邊圍福德堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/reA3N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FreA3N&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=72f010a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/reA3N</a><br />\n以下的畫面來自<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WB90VhmXytY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWB90VhmXytY&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=b4ad3eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WB90VhmXytY</a><br />\n<br />\n在當天凌晨 02:42:00 之後的影片都被刪除了<br />\n不知 Now 新聞台是否受到壓力<br />\n而以下的鏡頭是 Now 新聞台的攝影師躲在高架橋底下<br />\n用長鏡頭拍攝到的<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LQC6nCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLQC6nCq.jpg&h=eabe19f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q8XhJVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ8XhJVJ.jpg&h=9d94d11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8bOYrqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8bOYrqz.jpg&h=05d71e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CYOVO4n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCYOVO4n.jpg&h=223140a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YrKslRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYrKslRv.jpg&h=1283208f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察還來收回借給白衣人的棍棒<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VcmbaIf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVcmbaIf.jpg&h=1222e802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KrXBE55.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKrXBE55.jpg&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=a3aa5a7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/KrXBE55.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n其實還蠻像 1950 年代, 「聯合外省子弟們形成一個團體，並承襲古老幫會洪門與青幫的組織概念，及軍事家庭背景的管理模式，創立擁有組織架構的幫會，為當時中華民國政府吸收利用處理檯面上無法處置的問題，外省幫派因而迅速壯大」這次南邊圍也是為新統治者「幫忙處理檯面上無法處置的問題」, 看起來之後要飛黃騰達了<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qQYSV0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqQYSV0d.jpg&h=b76f106b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個畫面最妙, 白衣人和鎮暴警察一起聽某個人發言,雖然擋住了不知道是誰, 但可以看到大家都在往同個方向<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講這一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5zMswHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5zMswHQ.jpg&h=148691b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭髮理得像年輕人的白衣人穿回了刑警的背心, 真的蠻妙的<br />\n<br />\n另外昨日拍到放解放軍軍服的黑車抓到確定是白衣人持有了<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0cQvBAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0cQvBAx.jpg&h=1fb2d983&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:18:18.000Z","msg":"做市民幾時都要企硬對付黑警，總之無委任證就無身分證！"},{"pid":"0cfa7e80d6c88fad545731676a1d7603046beeff","tid":1377553,"uid":251551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:21:11.000Z","msg":"推 光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"36459b0635a5db9d652fcf5c42182c62c7665438","tid":1377553,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"967ce5712699a9cf3917cb001e400c54ec20953c","tid":1377553,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:22:37.000Z","msg":"比外國記者 白宮 英國"},{"pid":"1da448aec12c4181979b49c849d65669d229eb6a","tid":1377553,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:23:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd20feaf1f22150befe65ca14a4db2eaa76c5579","tid":1377553,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:23:47.000Z","msg":"推上報"},{"pid":"90ac7ee7e3e0a28102219acd9d467abec6142e08","tid":1377553,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:25:47.000Z","msg":"仲唔柒斷正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1662364dcc84595c73e9e213b6e0e12566649d8","tid":1377553,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab00f69ae5af6345bdd6e7e1dea6caa2496a3eb2","tid":1377553,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:35:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"068760c77227b63ffbe90e750549ef4d24c21628","tid":1377553,"uid":4619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:39:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ae34956a91995767e5d1a5b371c9dd4e3403fc2","tid":1377553,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:42:59.000Z","msg":"國共同源"},{"pid":"cf12602caa41cbcdb35a413ae027cc47ccee0dbd","tid":1377553,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci